title: Need help or have any ideas? Contact us!
header: We’re a small team, and if you have anything you’d like to discuss or anything you need help with in osekai, we’d be happy to help!
body.p1: The best way for you to contact us is to join the osu! Medal Hunters Discord.
body.p2: A link to this server is on the homepage & in the apps dropdown at the top left of the page.
snapshots: For any issues or requests regarding Osekai Snapshots, please contact Hubz at hubz@hubza.co.uk
